snippet.title: SNES Longplay [137] World Heroes
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org 

Played By: T-0815

This is my Longplay number 200! I never thought that I would ever make that many. My thanks to all members of our sites. My very special thanks goes to all the people who still love retro games. Thanks for all the feedback over the years. Until next time. Have fun!

Battle 01: - 01:16 - Rasputin 
Battle 02: - 03:32 - Janne
Battle 03: - 06:11 - Dragon
Battle 04: - 08:38 - M. Power
Battle 05: - 10:36 - J. Carn
Battle 06: - 13:01 - Hanzo
Battle 07: - 15:21 - Fuuma
